    "Name": "Badger 1",
    "Details": "The Badger is a mixed-tech evolution of the Abyss concept, trading Star League salvage for Clan-grade upgrades across the board. A Clan ER PPC and twin ER Medium Pulse Lasers handle direct fire at every range while an Artemis V-guided MML 7 adds flexible missile output. Five jump jets enable aggressive repositioning that the original Abyss could never manage, and an Angel ECM suite layers electronic disruption over the whole package.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Accurate Weapon - Missiles</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.16</color></b>",
